=Computers+%26+Education&amp;rft.atitle=Bring+Your+Own+Device+%28BYOD%29+for+seamless+science+inquiry+in+a+primary+school&amp;rft.volume=74&amp;rft.pages=50+60&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1016%2Fj.compedu.2014.01.005&amp;rft.aulast=Song&amp;rft.aufirst=Yanjie&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0360131514000153&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASocial+media+in+education\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raths_2012_28-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Raths_2012_28_6-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Raths_2012_28_6-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Raths, David (2012). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.questia.com/library/journal/1G1-292008620/are-you-ready-for-byod-advice-from-the-trenches-on\">\"Are You Ready for BYOD: Advice from the Trenches on How to Prepare Your Wireless Network for the Bring-Your-Own-Device Movement\"</a>. <i>THE Journal (Technological Horizons In Education)</i>. <b>39</b> (4): 28.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=THE+Journal+%28Technological+Horizons+In+Education%29&amp;rft.atitle=Are+You+Ready+for+BYOD%3A+Advice+from+the+Trenches+on+How+to+Prepare+Your+Wireless+Network+for+the+Bring-Your-Own-Device+Movement&amp;rft.volume=39&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=28&amp;rft.date=2012&amp;rft.aulast=Raths&amp;rft.aufirst=David&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.questia.com%2Flibrary%2Fjournal%2F1G1-292008620%2Fare-you-ready-for-byod-advice-from-the-trenches-on&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASocial+media+in+education\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Schwartz, S. O.; Rhodes, J. E.; Liang, B.; Sanchez, B. Spencer; Kremer, S.; Kanchewa, S. (2014). \"Mentoring in the digital age: Social Media use in adult-youth relationships\". <i>Children and Youth Services Review</i>. <b>47</b> (3): 205\u2013213. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1016/j.childyouth.2014.09.004\">10.1016/j.childyouth.2014.09.004</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Children+and+Youth+Services+Review&amp;rft.atitle=Mentoring+in+the+digital+age%3A+Social+Media+use+in+adult-youth+relationships&amp;rft.volume=47&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=205-213&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1016%2Fj.childyouth.2014.09.004&amp;rft.aulast=Schwartz&amp;rft.aufirst=S.+O.&amp;rft.au=Rhodes%2C+J.+E.&amp;rft.au=Liang%2C+B.&amp;rft.au=Sanchez%2C+B.+Spencer&amp;rft.au=Kremer%2C+S.&amp;rft.au=Kanchewa%2C+S.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASocial+media+in+education\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Kolb, Liz (2008). <i>Toys to tools&#160;: connecting student cell phones to education</i>. Eugene, Or.: International Society for Technology in Education. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1564842473\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-1564842473\">978-1564842473</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Toys+to+tools+%3A+connecting+student+cell